node.accessibility_caption: Homemade brown butter brownies

node.text:
Why have just regular brownies when you can enjoy BROWN BUTTER Brownies?! 😏👌🏻 This recipe is ultra rich, chewy, and fudgy with that classic shiny crinkly crust on top and gooey chocolate chips inside 🙌🏻🤤 For the recipe and my secrets for that crinkly crust, tap the link in my bio @handletheheat + click on this photo 🍫⁠⠀⁠⁠⁠⁠
